songs.title: Private Audition
songs.lyrics:
...with sass
Want you to pump up my ride
'Cause we're drivin' all night
I like a, a little licky when my lipgloss is sticky
Give me a hickey...

Move it, move it (What?)
If you want me you better prove it, prove it (Let's go)
I need your measurements to know if, know if (What?)
I wanna take you home and do it
